1
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:26,708
[RURAL GIRL AND
RURAL BOY LAUGH]

2
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:33,750
[RURAL MAN GASPS]

3
00:02:41,958 --> 00:02:44,250
Shichiroji...

4
00:02:44,333 --> 00:02:47,583
We're going to drive straight
into that enemy battleship...

5
00:02:47,666 --> 00:02:52,375
Buy some time for our allies.
So they can retreat safely.

6
00:02:52,458 --> 00:02:53,625
A losing battle, huh?

7
00:02:53,708 --> 00:02:55,250
[KAMBEI]
It's all we've got.

8
00:02:55,333 --> 00:02:57,833
Commander, flip the
Pressure-Valves to wide open.

9
00:02:57,916 --> 00:03:02,166
Propulsion Drive to Maximum.
Pulse Armor on Forward Defense.

10
00:03:02,250 --> 00:03:03,875
We're going in.

11
00:03:45,625 --> 00:03:47,291
[YELLING]

12
00:04:56,875 --> 00:05:02,375
[PERCUSSIVE CHIMING]

13
00:05:02,458 --> 00:05:03,666
[VILLAGERS CHANT]

14
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:06,333
[KIRARA] ♪ Patient
looking, ardent search, ♪

15
00:05:06,416 --> 00:05:11,083
♪ Searching for the truth... ♪

16
